 - Create a system in which users can login, users can be of two types. 1 - Managers, 2- Employees.
 - Managers can assign task to their employees, employees can make transitions to tasks, such as 
   in-progress, on-hold, completed. 
 - Manager should be able to view the task summary of employees under him, different managers 
   will have different employees, and each manager will have access to only employees who work under him.
 - Managers should not be able to make any state transitions to their subordinates' tasks.
 - managers will be able to add their own employees, and avanga add panna employees dhan avanga keezha work panra employees